  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Be on sick leave

          -  Have moderate to severe affective and / or moderate / severe anxiety disorder, such
             as: Bipolar disorder, depression, posttraumatic stress disorder, generalized anxiety
             disorder, neuropsychiatric disability

          -  Enrolled at the Academic hospital in Uppsala

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  High suicidal risk

          -  Extensive somatic disorders (somatic multichannel)

          -  Patients outside Uppsala County

          -  Taking part in an ongoing vocational rehabilitation
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
